SUMMARY:🌙 Pre-Sleep (Susu Hangat + Kurma)
DESCRIPTION:Susu hangat + 2-3 kurma + 1 sdt madu.\nKurma membantu kontraksi optimal mendekati persalinan (QS. Maryam 19:25).\nMadu mengandung obat (QS. An-Nahl 16:69).\n\nReferensi: Sadeghi 2019 PMID:31331586\, HR. Bukhari 5681
